      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "See also #10554. This older PR is apparently both used in production by its author, @somdoron, as well as included in Bitcoin Knots. For that reason, it would be ideal to use an interface compatible with it if reasonably possible - I think simply putting the hash as the first item might work; maybe multipart too? (not sure)\r\n\r\nNote it's called -zmqpub**hash**wallettx there (and a raw variant provided). I'm not sure if the raw variant is as easily extended to include a wallet name - that might require the multipart stuff.",
